metadata.name: Σίσυφος
metadata.description:
Push hard to reach the highest,
Fall to the bottom instantly.
Some people try to escape,
Some enjoy being trapped.

Immersed in the world of NFT,
Sisyphean circle seems to be our daily,
As some kind of non-fungible memory.

－Σίσυφος・DEBRIS OF MEMORY #1
